adept.common

Class TokenOffset

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.TokenOffset

  • public final class TokenOffset
extends Object
    The TokenOffset class captures begin and end integer positions of character or token spans. Both begin and end offsets are inclusive. This class is immutable.
